<section>
  <h1 class="text-5xl font-semibold">
    Hi I'm Igor<br/>
    I'm a Fullstack Developer
  </h1>
  <.p>
    I build modern web applications with a focus on<br />
    performance and user experience.
  </.p>
  <button class="mt-5 px-6 py-2 bg-teal-600 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-teal-700 transition shadow-md 
    bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_center,_#0d9488,_#0f766e)] 
    hover:brightness-110">
    See Projects
  </button>
</section>
<section class="mt-20 border-t border-gray-500 pt-5">
  <.h2>
    About
  </.h2>
  <.p>
    I am a developer with experience in building high-quality web applications.<br />
    I enjoy solving challenging problems and learning new technologies.
  </.p>
</section>
